		</li>
		<li>
			8. <span class="primary">Sesokhris</span> ruled 48 years. It is said that he was five cubits and three palms (about eight and one-half feet) tall.8
		</li>
		<li>9. <span class="primary">Kheneres</span> ruled 30 years. Under the ninth king nothing worth mention happened.</li>
	</ul>
